text: South Terminal () is a 2019 French drama film directed by Rabah Ameur- Zaïmeche. It was screened in the Contemporary World Cinema section at the 2019 Toronto International Film Festival. ==Cast== * Ramzy Bedia * Amel Brahim- Djelloul * Slimane Dazi * Vanessa Liautey * Jacques Nolot ==References== ==External links== * Category:2019 films Category:2019 drama films Category:French films Category:French drama films Category:French-language films
